name: Space Rage Program!
description:
Rage Space Program is my entry for the EpicMegaJam2019. I was done in my leasure time in a week all by myself.

Control your frustration and try to reach the top to retrieve a Sputnik. Then, make your way back home safely. Ho, and by the way, you have 5 minutes!

Not for the faint of heart.

Have fun!
